{"id":154627,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/科学家想象中世界末时的样子/","date":"2011-05-23T11:11:44Z","modified":"2011-05-23T11:11:44Z","title":"科学家想象中世界末时的样子","content":"<p><p>原作者：<br />来源<a href=\"http://www.yeeyan.org/\">科学者が予測　世界終末の地球の様子</a><br />译者<a href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/135134\">强制作</a></p>\n<p><strong><span>科学家想象中世界末时的样子</span></strong></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-05/23/20110523160538_17306.jpg\" border=\"0\" /><br /> <strong>大火和洪水袭击着整座城市。</strong></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-05/23/20110523160556_87367.jpg\" border=\"0\" /><br /> <strong>洪水向整座城市奔涌而来，巨浪涛天，势不可挡。</strong></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-05/23/20110523160507_38302.jpg\" border=\"0\" /><br /> <strong>铺天盖地，吞没一切。</strong></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-05/23/20110523160515_52046.jpg\" border=\"0\" /><br /> <strong>整座城市沉没于水下。</strong></p>\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-05/23/20110523160523_99939.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></strong></p>\n<p><strong>摧枯拉朽，横扫一切。</strong></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-05/23/20110523160532_11373.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<p><strong>威力无比，洪水倾刻间将整座城池变为人间地狱。</strong></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-05/23/20110523160541_71016.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<p><strong>电闪雷鸣，瓢泼大雨，如注而下。</strong></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-05/23/20110523160553_88545.jpg\" border=\"0\" /><br /> <strong>惊天动地，令人惊魂魄散！</strong></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-05/23/20110523160505_87889.jpg\" border=\"0\" /><br /> <strong>天旋地转，土崩瓦解，分崩离析.</strong></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://cdn.yeeyan.org/upload/attached/2011-05/23/20110523160516_15129.jpg\" border=\"0\" /><br /> <strong>葬身海底，一切归于寂静。</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://ar